        "description": "All experimental test conditions documented with traceability to ISO 14243-1 (wear testing) and ISO 14243-3 (displacement control). Synovial fluid simulant composition, temperature, and loading waveforms recorded and archived. Uncertainty in applied load < 2%, displacement < 0.1 mm."
      },
      "rationale": "µPIV experiments conducted in ISO-controlled environment. Gait loading waveform from ISO 14243-3 applied via servo-hydraulic test frame (MTS 858 Mini Bionix). Synovial fluid simulant: 25% bovine calf serum at 37 ± 0.5 °C. Load cell calibration traceable to NIST. All test parameters logged at 1 kHz and archived in the institutional data repository."
