        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Use error Level 2 — documented simulation protocol with independent review",
        "description": "A documented simulation protocol specifying all boundary conditions, material properties, solver settings, and post-processing steps must be reviewed by a second qualified engineer not involved in the original setup. Deviations from protocol must be logged."
      },
      "rationale": "Simulation protocol document (SOP-CFD-TKR-001 Rev B) reviewed and approved by a second CFD engineer (Dr. P. Ramirez, PE). Protocol covers all boundary condition specifications, mesh generation parameters, solver settings, and post-processing scripts. No deviations from protocol were logged during the COU1 assessment runs. Level 2 achieved."
