      "rationale": "Test samples factor is scoped out for this COU1 assessment. The validation strategy relies on µPIV and LDV measurements in a precision-machined silicone phantom representing the tibial tray geometry, not on explanted or production implant samples. Phantom dimensional accuracy (±0.1 mm, CT-verified) is documented under Test Conditions. A separate COU2 assessment addresses explant retrieval analysis and will include Test Samples evaluation at MRL 3."
    },
    {
